Package semsim.reading

Class OMEXmetadataReader

java.lang.Object
semsim.reading.AbstractRDFreader
semsim.reading.OMEXmetadataReader
public class OMEXmetadataReader
extends AbstractRDFreader
Class for working with annotations stored in Combine Archive annotation (OMEX metadata) files. OMEX metadata files are standalone RDF files in COMBINE archives that are used to house annotations on models within the archive.
Author:
mneal

      Constructor
      Parameters:
      ma - A ModelAccessor indicating the location of the OMEX metadata file
      semsimmodel - The SemSimModel to annotate using the contents of the OMEX metadata file
      lib - A SemSimLibrary instance
      rdfstring - Additional RDF content to include in the model's metadata that is not contained in the OMEX metadata file (e.g. curatorial info in a CellML model.
